			role="button" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1" title="Connexion GitHub — bientôt disponible">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6 opacity-40">
